CREATE TABLE demographics(
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    income DECIMAL
);
CREATE TABLE address(
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    street_address TEXT,
    city VARCHAR(50),
    state VARCHAR(2),
    country VARCHAR(50)
);
CREATE TABLE education(
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    level VARCHAR(20),
    major VARCHAR(50),
    graduation_year INT,
    institution VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE demographics (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    city VARCHAR(50),
    state VARCHAR(50),
    population INT,
    median_income DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE social_status (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    education_level VARCHAR(50),
    occupation VARCHAR(50),
    income DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE housing (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    property_type VARCHAR(50),
    num_bedrooms INT,
    square_footage INT
);

CREATE TABLE neighborhood (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,

    crime_rate DECIMAL(10,2),
    poverty_rate DECIMAL(10,2),
    home_value DECIMAL(10,2)
);
